| Shift | SOBRECARGA | 12.8 s | 3.2 s time acceleration: +60% speed/fire-rate/bullets, 0.6× gravity |
| E | RANIBOBER | 2.5 s / stack (max 8) | Rewind to stored frame: teleport, 50% heal, 5 m / 40 DMG AoE, bubble rewind |

